{
  "abstract": "This note is intended to serve as a basis for a\r\nthorough discussion about the role of an International Institute\r\nsuch as ICRISAT in the area of Farming Systems Research. As such\r\nit is very tentative and the ideas expressed need scrutiny,\r\nqualification and amplification by researchers inside and outside\r\nof the International system. However the issues involved are of\r\nextreme importance for the successful allocation of research\r\nresources and research tasks within the international system and\r\nbetween the national and international systems.",
